{"tid":1504931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「分撚化夠未」笑撚夠未呀你班冷氣垃圾","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T15:04:22.000Z","uid":53803,"like":211,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"0078bc0a6f365c975f37f76644677f56fbc83cb7","tid":1504931,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"十個post有九個都笑鳩勇武張相<br />\n你知唔知幾撚難同班防暴佬打呀<br />\n張相背後係架水炮車呀<br />\n剩係識得笑笑笑<br />\n行完翻屋企又話冇撚用，政府唔撚聽<br />\n行完Set RB，又屌好唔走，送頭<br />\nBe Water狗鐵又封柒曬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚憎「送頭」呢兩個字<br />\n落到場根本係兩回事，<br />\n成日望勇武手足打贏差佬俾你班連登仔打J<br />\n我唔撚明點解我每次出完去翻黎連登都係一面倒屌<br />\n你班垃圾勝利球迷食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌撚曬你地老母呀<br />\n<br />\n成日問問問有乜意義<br />\n咁係咪日日和理非就最撚有意義呀<br />\n係現場post問咁有乜野做<br />\n又個個話前線決定<br />\n你地玩撚曬啦屌你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班連登仔好似捧隊波咁<br />\n踢得好就打J<br />\n踢得差就屌到地底泥<br />\n冷氣軍師收皮縮翻入老母個閪到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線冇人睇到你地up乜柒 亦都冇上帝視覺<br />\n我認為今後勇武心灰意冷 都係連登仔一手累成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8818a8e33804fb759a9c07216cc2c988bb3f8b06","tid":1504931,"uid":53803,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係好撚痛心"},{"pid":"2300f46a55b567a4a9a656242c99e2309fd3ebba","tid":1504931,"uid":53803,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"成也連登敗也連登"},{"pid":"80db7b64e3e3a7435ca1bf5da09321347acf1984","tid":1504931,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbeca16743798b2ab0a48d641f7e180be14b50a","tid":1504931,"uid":2419,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"放心 開post笑果班全部都冇落過場"},{"pid":"65c2c3ef8fd8089cc3bcfd5d532409e37f060517","tid":1504931,"uid":44461,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n其實我見個啲咩 5點鬆啲呀 6點鬆啲呀 總知7點前開post屌自己友個啲<br />\n根本就唔係現場 好有可能係屋企涼緊冷氣 開兩個live 就以為自己係諸葛亮 左一句送頭 右一句唔識be water咁樣車埋去 笑大人個口咩 今日有係現場嘅一定知 如果7點前你可以拎到部電話出黎 開埋啲垃圾post 一係你就一早就走左 一係你就根本係屋企涼緊冷氣<br />\n<br />\n細個爸爸媽媽有無教你地?如果有人幫你做野 代你俾人拉 代你獻出生命去對抗呢個極權 你係要講多謝 唔係 「送頭」 亦都唔係咩 「心痛」"},{"pid":"514756168c170d652b2401518667b4745c1131a2","tid":1504931,"uid":37234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"f3ea6043ce94545b31781cf6eb7fa298e725a001","tid":1504931,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"874efadb4c22504d2295d27787e67d914f91fe20","tid":1504931,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"人會進化學習<br />\n冷氣軍師唔好嘈"},{"pid":"e19891a14683cd21e32d1e4ee9df70cc7620ac50","tid":1504931,"uid":117968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3712538e10c09f13b9a968f4f69a6c112d45ba32","tid":1504931,"uid":53803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"今日好撚難打呀師兄<br />\n你估唔撚想打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c49d1772e3ea1882825f8783bd9efb71174f494","tid":1504931,"uid":9699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"點解 點解呢兩日退步玩返對峙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504591</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇下E個po班冷氣軍師係度圍爐屌勇武對峙唔肯走唔敢還擊<br />\n<br />\n靠佢地香港一早好似2014咁輸左啦"},{"pid":"12eb525c300ef93972bc2c887186c1d3ba1e2004","tid":1504931,"uid":53803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師出少句聲當幫忙"},{"pid":"3c91b21c86bcdfe09a80da0fbf251ce2367ad21b","tid":1504931,"uid":22566,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班撚樣 靠把口有用 行行企企有用就唔撚使搞兩個幾月啦 究竟知唔知面對緊咩政權呀 唔係要分化 而係有啲事情 必須有所犧牲 要怪就怪香港人以前淨係得個錢字 完全唔理政治</span></span>"},{"pid":"152ab7c373d0f681f814fc13a7120a45eae125c2","tid":1504931,"uid":17958,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:20:42.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師真係好撚on9"},{"pid":"f271122eca3a56a66d91507c7d78db75f25afdd8","tid":1504931,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:20:48.000Z","msg":"反送中運動之後要點行之我見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504835</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c594dddcdcf8421efe824d2316b673eb25862455","tid":1504931,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:20:51.000Z","msg":"咪撚再打擊士氣"},{"pid":"e8c3f815141007ad7cc130e8532926ad840acdee","tid":1504931,"uid":47402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35990b374b67c5e1fd32fe25b68ee0cb916af4fd","tid":1504931,"uid":53803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"和理非贏盡掌聲 咁得到啲乜"},{"pid":"9f3f9b6cbd9d77b2d696f3441c747391b787bfab","tid":1504931,"uid":73862,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"你有眼睇<br />\n後排果d食花生<br />\n逼到前線果d走唔切<br />\n你諗下啦 d狗全身裝備本身好難跑得快過手足<br />\n就係因為比人頂撚住ja"},{"pid":"b1f9caa3a17883d97278227ed711ff8dc9e2e6c8","tid":1504931,"uid":186072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"軍師?<br />\n佢地幫過咩手?<br />\n係屋企睇住live黎屌咋<br 